    p The summer holidays are in full swing, and WOW what a summer we’re having! Holiday Club is bigger, better and more popular than ever! So popular that we welcome a brand new play worker Eden to our team to accommodate this year’s high demand! We've added more spaces, so please logon to #[a(href='https://libacura.co.uk') Libacura] to view availability and book.
    
